[[edit](/w/index.php?title=Network_Manager&action=edit&section=1 "Edit section: Installation")] Installation
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To enable NetworkManager service in NixOS:

       networking.networkmanager.enable = true;

User needs to be in **networkmanager** group in order to control
networkmanager configuration.

### [[edit](/w/index.php?title=Network_Manager&action=edit&section=2 "Edit section: GTK applet")] GTK applet

To use **nm-applet**, you have to install **networkmanagerapplet**.

### [[edit](/w/index.php?title=Network_Manager&action=edit&section=3 "Edit section: KDE applet")] KDE applet

The Network Manager widget for KDE is available in nixpkgs as
**kde4.networkmanagement**.

